How to run uvm on SM. I put in an helper script.

Run this script
sh build_run_uvm.sh

OR, do it individually


1)  For Compiling IPs and Subsystems, execute: “gmake -f Makefile_VCS.mk cmplib_adp" 
2)  Hack some files (pim, hssi) - look at build_run_uvm.sh
2)  For building RTL & TB, execute: “gmake -f Makefile_VCS.mk build_adp DUMP=1 DEBUG=1"
3)  For run, execute: “gmake -f Makefile_VCS.mk run TESTNAME=mmio_test DUMP=1 DEBUG=1 ”
